<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 00:50:40 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>快速双杀让阿尔希拉尔在亚洲冠军联赛中占据优势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/quick-fire-double-gives-al-hilal-advantage-asian-champions-league-2024-03-06/</link><description>下周，阿尔希拉尔队将在与沙特职业联赛球队阿尔伊蒂哈德队的亚洲冠军联赛四分之一决赛第二回合比赛中以 2-0 领先，上半场两分钟内的两粒进球为这支利雅得球队带来了健康的表现。周二优势。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 00:34:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/quick-fire-double-gives-al-hilal-advantage-asian-champions-league-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>南海紧张局势下东盟峰会聚焦海上安全和贸易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-summit-focus-maritime-security-trade-amid-south-china-sea-tensions-2024-03-06/</link><description>澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴内斯周三表示，随着北京寻求加强其在有争议的南海的存在，海上安全、贸易和清洁能源将塑造该国与东盟的未来。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 00:23:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-summit-focus-maritime-security-trade-amid-south-china-sea-tensions-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国习近平召唤“新生产力”，但老问题依然存在</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-xi-summons-new-productive-forces-old-questions-linger-economy-2024-03-05/</link><description>面对多年来最严峻的经济挑战，中国领导层已责成各部委和地方政府落实习近平主席的新口号：释放“新生产力”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 23:03:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-xi-summons-new-productive-forces-old-questions-linger-economy-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>早间买盘：风险反弹突然停止</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-03-05/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 21:49:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>参议员卢比奥寻求提高关税以阻止中国“涌入美国汽车市场”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/senator-rubio-seeks-stiffer-tariff-stop-china-flooding-us-auto-markets-2024-03-05/</link><description>美国共和党参议员卢比奥周二提议大幅提高中国汽车进口关税2万美元，以阻止中国“涌入美国汽车市场”，这是华盛顿保护美国汽车制造商和汽车工人的最新举措。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 21:33:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/senator-rubio-seeks-stiffer-tariff-stop-china-flooding-us-auto-markets-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟将允许对中国电动汽车征收追溯关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-set-allow-possible-retroactive-tariffs-chinese-evs-2024-03-05/</link><description>欧盟委员会计划开始对中国电动汽车（EV）进口进行海关登记，这意味着如果欧盟的贸易调查随后得出结论认为它们正在接受不公平补贴，那么从那时起它们可能会受到关税打击。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 21:20:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-set-allow-possible-retroactive-tariffs-chinese-evs-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>比亚迪引领中国电动汽车进军澳大利亚这个更加友好的市场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/byd-spearheads-chinese-electric-car-push-australia-friendlier-market-2024-03-05/</link><description>比亚迪和其他中国汽车制造商正在向澳大利亚大量推出新的电动汽车车型，在澳大利亚市场，他们没有面临贸易壁垒，而且由于电动汽车补贴和税收优惠以及高汽油价格，销量激增。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 21:05:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/byd-spearheads-chinese-electric-car-push-australia-friendlier-market-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>立法者寻求迫使字节跳动剥离 TikTok，否则将面临美国禁令</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/lawmakers-seek-force-bytedance-divest-tiktok-or-face-us-ban-2024-03-05/</link><description>美国两党议员小组周二提出立法，给予中国字节跳动约六个月的时间剥离流行短视频应用 TikTok，否则将面临美国禁令。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 17:14:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/lawmakers-seek-force-bytedance-divest-tiktok-or-face-us-ban-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯称正在考虑与中国合作在月球上建设核电站</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/russia-china-are-considering-putting-nuclear-power-unit-moon-ria-2024-03-05/</link><description>俄罗斯航天局局长尤里·鲍里索夫周二表示，俄罗斯和中国正在考虑从 2033 年至 35 年在月球上建造一座核电站，他表示，有一天可能会允许在月球上建造定居点。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 12:28:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/russia-china-are-considering-putting-nuclear-power-unit-moon-ria-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>法国“蜘蛛侠”攀登塔楼支持菲律宾南海主张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/french-spiderman-scales-tower-support-philippines-south-china-sea-claims-2024-03-05/</link><description>周二，一名被称为“法国蜘蛛侠”的自由攀登者爬上了马尼拉的一座摩天大楼，以支持菲律宾在有争议的南中国海的海洋主张。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 10:36:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/french-spiderman-scales-tower-support-philippines-south-china-sea-claims-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>独家：碧桂园贷款人集团聘请顾问进行债务重组谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/country-garden-lenders-group-hires-advisers-debt-revamp-talks-sources-say-2024-03-05/</link><description>三位知情人士称，中国碧桂园的一组贷款人已聘请安理国际会计师事务所(Allen &amp;amp; Overy)和德勤(Deloitte)作为顾问，而这家陷入困境的开发商的债权人正在为可能的债务重组谈判做好准备。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 09:24:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/country-garden-lenders-group-hires-advisers-debt-revamp-talks-sources-say-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>台湾敦促与中国进行无政治先决条件的对话</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-urges-dialogue-with-china-without-political-preconditions-2024-03-05/</link><description>北京在一份政府工作报告中强化了在台湾问题上的立场后，台湾陆委会周二敦促中国接受两岸互不隶属的事实。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 08:46:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-urges-dialogue-with-china-without-political-preconditions-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾、美国将在面向南海和台湾的岛屿举行军事演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-us-hold-military-drills-islands-facing-south-china-sea-taiwan-2024-03-05/</link><description>随着该地区与中国的紧张局势持续发酵，菲律宾和美国将于下个月在菲律宾面临南海的岛屿和台湾等关键地点举行年度军事演习。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 07:49:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-us-hold-military-drills-islands-facing-south-china-sea-taiwan-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>华为人气飙升，苹果 iPhone 在中国销量暴跌 24%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apples-china-iphone-sales-plunge-24-first-six-weeks-2024-report-says-2024-03-05/</link><description>研究公司 Counterpoint 的数据显示，2024 年前六周，苹果 iPhone 在中国的销量同比下降了 24%，因为这家美国公司面临着来自华为 (HWT.UL) 等国内竞争对手的日益激烈的竞争。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 07:22:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apples-china-iphone-sales-plunge-24-first-six-weeks-2024-report-says-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>由于财政火箭弹难以捉摸，中国投资者坚持逢低买入</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/investors-china-stick-bargains-fiscal-bazooka-proves-elusive-2024-03-05/</link><description>重返正在复苏的中国股市的外国投资者表示，周二宣布的支出计划不足以扭转低迷的情绪，目前继续购买股票的主要原因是它们价格便宜。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 07:20:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/investors-china-stick-bargains-fiscal-bazooka-proves-elusive-2024-03-05/</guid></item></channel></rss>